## Storage Capacitance 

$$ C_s = \epsilon A \sqrt{\frac{q}{2 \epsilon (V_0 - V_a)} \frac{N_a N_d}{N_a + N_d}} $$

## Storage vs Junction capacitance:

- FORWARD BIAS: $C_j <<  C_s$
- REVERSE BIAS: $C_j >> C_s$

